snippet.title: The Jackbox Party Pack Trailer - PS4,PS3,XboxOne,Steam,FireTV, & Nexus Player available NOW!
snippet.description:
http://jackboxgames.com/app/the-jackbox-party-pack/

Available NOW on PS4, PS3, Xbox One, PC Steam, Amazon Fire TV and Fire TV Stick, and the Nexus Player! For 1-100 players! Your phones or tablets are your controllers! The team behind YOU DON’T KNOW JACK presents FIVE guffaw-inducing party games in one pack! You’re gonna need more than one party for this.

http://jackboxgames.com/app/the-jackbox-party-pack/
